  "title": "Retail Salesperson",
  "description": "<h3>Who We Are</h3><p>Dr J is a Singapore-based company established since 2010, specialising in locally designed and manufactured foot orthotic arches and footwear. We help customers improve comfort, alignment, and mobility from the ground up.</p><h3>Job Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Assist customers with footwear and foot arch solutions<br /><br /></p></li><li><p>Explain product features and proper usage confidently<br /><br /></p></li><li><p>Provide friendly, patient, and professional customer service<br /><br /></p></li></ul><p><p><p><p>Support daily retail operations and store upkeep<br /><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p></p><p><p>Local or Permanent Residents only (Applicants must be eligible to work in Singapore without requiring a work permit or visa)</p></p><p><p>Bilingual </p></p><p><p>Comfortable interacting with customers<br /><br /></p></p><p><p>Willing to learn — training provided<br /><br /></p></p><p>Able to work weekends (Saturday & Sunday)<br /><br /><strong>Working Hours</strong></p><p><p>5 or 6-day work week<br /><br /></p></p><p><p>11:00am – 9:00pm (1 hour lunch break)<br /><br /><strong>What We Offer</strong><br /><br />- Full product & sales training provided<br />- Stable retail environment<br />-Opportunity to learn about footwear & foot health<br />-Conditional AWS (13th month bonus)</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></p></p></p>",
